name: Come Healing
description:
The splinters that you carry
The cross you left behind
Come healing of the body
Come healing of the mind

O solitude of longing
Where love has been confined
Come healing of the body
Come healing of the mind 

( Leonard Cohen )

To develop this film, I had to use product already used, it made most of the photos completely sanded, with an incredible grain. For many these photos are screwed up, but I like damaged things, their beauty to be there, the presence in them shows itself even more clearly.
